cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.RO 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning, decision making, and preference-based RL, which are all topics that fall under the machine learning and artificial intelligence umbrella. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses game theory and multi-agent systems, which are relevant to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Finally, the paper touches on robotics, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics).
